=== Therefore the Plan: The United States Federal Government should amend the Coastal Zone Management Act to include an explicit mandate for offshore wind power development where appropriate and feasible on all U.S. coasts and require revisions to Coastal Zone Management Plans in accordance with this new mandate. The United States Federal Government should also extend and expand the Investment Tax Credit for offshore wind programs. ===

